---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/main.astro';
---

<MainLayout content={{ title: 'Opportunities | AI Secure Software Development' }}>
  <section class="container mx-auto py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Opportunities</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-12">
      <p class="text-lg mb-8">
        Join our team and contribute to cutting-edge research in AI-powered secure software development. 
        We offer various opportunities for researchers, students, and industry professionals to collaborate 
        and make a meaningful impact in the field of software security.
      </p>
      
      <!-- Research Positions Section -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Research Positions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Position Item -->
          <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Postdoctoral Researcher - AI Security</h3>
              <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">
                Full-time
              </span>
            </div>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We are seeking a postdoctoral researcher with expertise in AI and software security to join our team. 
              The successful candidate will lead research projects focused on developing AI-powered tools for 
              secure software development.
            </p>
            <div class="mb-4">
              <h4 class="font-medium mb-2">Requirements:</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-muted-foreground">
                <li>PhD in Computer Science or related field</li>
                <li>Strong background in machine learning and software security</li>
                <li>Experience with programming language analysis</li>
                <li>Excellent publication record</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary hover:text-primary/80">
              Apply Now
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-1"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Position Item -->
          <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Research Scientist - Secure Code Generation</h3>
              <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">
                Full-time
              </span>
            </div>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We are looking for a research scientist to work on our secure code generation project. 
              The role involves developing and evaluating AI models that can generate secure code and 
              provide security-focused recommendations to developers.
            </p>
            <div class="mb-4">
              <h4 class="font-medium mb-2">Requirements:</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-muted-foreground">
                <li>MSc or PhD in Computer Science or related field</li>
                <li>Experience with large language models and code generation</li>
                <li>Knowledge of software security principles and common vulnerabilities</li>
                <li>Strong programming skills in Python and JavaScript/TypeScript</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary hover:text-primary/80">
              Apply Now
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-1"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Student Opportunities Section -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Student Opportunities</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Opportunity Item -->
          <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">PhD Studentship - AI for Software Security</h3>
              <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">
                Full-time
              </span>
            </div>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We offer fully funded PhD studentships for exceptional candidates interested in pursuing research 
              in AI-powered secure software development. Students will work on cutting-edge projects under the 
              supervision of leading researchers in the field.
            </p>
            <div class="mb-4">
              <h4 class="font-medium mb-2">Requirements:</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-muted-foreground">
                <li>MSc in Computer Science or related field</li>
                <li>Strong academic record</li>
                <li>Background in machine learning, software engineering, or security</li>
                <li>Excellent programming skills</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary hover:text-primary/80">
              Apply Now
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-1"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Opportunity Item -->
          <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Summer Research Internship</h3>
              <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">
                Temporary
              </span>
            </div>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Our summer research internship program offers undergraduate and master's students the opportunity 
              to work on real research projects in AI-powered secure software development. Interns will collaborate 
              with our research team and gain valuable experience in the field.
            </p>
            <div class="mb-4">
              <h4 class="font-medium mb-2">Requirements:</h4>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-muted-foreground">
                <li>Currently enrolled in a Computer Science or related degree program</li>
                <li>Knowledge of machine learning or software security</li>
                <li>Programming experience in Python, JavaScript, or Java</li>
                <li>Strong problem-solving skills</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary hover:text-primary/80">
              Apply Now
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-1"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Industry Collaboration Section -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Industry Collaboration</h2>
        <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <p class="mb-4">
            We welcome collaboration with industry partners interested in advancing the field of secure software 
            development. Our team works with companies of all sizes to develop and evaluate AI-powered security 
            tools that address real-world challenges.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-6">
            If you are interested in partnering with us, please get in touch to discuss potential collaboration 
            opportunities.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary hover:text-primary/80">
            Contact Us
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-1"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout> 